            g.nodes.Add(new DialogueNode { id = "cal_deal_crit", speaker = "Calloway", text = "*(You don't just spot the hook — you *seize* it, and turn it, and lay his own logic on the felt between you so precisely that for one perfect second the most charming soul in the afterlife is simply, genuinely *outplayed* — and his face, when it comes, is not anger and not chagrin but pure, delighted, almost *paternal* *joy.*)* …*oh.* …*ohh*, that's — *(he actually applauds, three slow claps)* …you *clever*, *clever* *creature.* you didn't *haggle* the *price* *down* — *anyone* *haggles* the *price* — you *re*-*priced* the *whole* *table*, you made me *see* that a *Returned* who can *do* *that* is worth *infinitely* *more* to *Calloway* as a *friend* who *owes* him *nothing* than a *mark* who owes him *one.* *(he sweeps the bone-white marker off the felt and, instead, slides it *across* to you, and closes your fingers around it)* …*take* it. *free.* *no* *debt.* *no* *string.* …a *gift*, cold one, from the *house* — and i *promise* you, on the *one* *soul* i *own* *outright*, *which* is *mine*, that gift is the *most* *expensive* thing i've *given* away in *four* *hundred* *years*, and *worth* *every* *uncharged* *coin.* …*(he leans in, and the warmth is, terrifyingly, *real*)* …i *deal* to *gods*, friend. and *not* *one* of *them* …ever made me *want* to *break* my *own* *rules* …just to *keep* *talking* to *them.* …*you* *did.* …the *door* *that* *marker* *opens* is *yours.* …and so, *gods* *help* *me*, is a *favor* — *mine* to *you*, *unspecified*, *your* *call* — because a soul who can *out*-*deal* *Calloway* …is a soul i'd *very* *much* rather have *holding* my *marker* …than the *other* way *round.* …*don't* *tell* *anyone.* …it'd *ruin* me.", onEnter = new[] { new FlagClause { key = "cal.haggled", op = FlagOp.SetTrue }, new FlagClause { key = "cal.outdealt_calloway", op = FlagOp.SetTrue }, new FlagClause { key = "cal.calloway_owes_you", op = FlagOp.SetTrue }, new Fl